This Access Request case was submitted on {!Get_Case.BPS_Plan_Submitted_to_NDIA__c}.


Record an Activity Log - You need to log that:

  • You have spoken with the customer in regards to this Access Request case OR
  • You have completed an admin task associated with this Access Request case OR
  • The customer has provided further information after it was requested by the NDIA

Enter Access Decision - You need to log that:

  • An access decision has been made OR
  • The NDIA have requested further information from the customer OR
  • The NDIA have returned the Access Request case as it is incomplete
